            </p>

            <div className="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a href="https://github.com/shahriar-shahram" className="accent-button inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition">
                <FaGithub className="h-4 w-4" />
